    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ Lord, Thy ho-ly Mar-tyrs, since they had for-got-ten all that is but earth--ly, com-plete-ly set at nought most bit-ter tor--ments for the e-ter-nal life to come. Now__ they have in-her-it-ed that life a-bove; where--fore, they re-joice with the an-gel-ic hosts. In-cline to their en-treat-ies, grant--ing un-to Thy peo-ple great mer-cy through__ their__ prayers."
    }
